task.summary:
Some changes in the UI : The main layout doesn't contain the drawer
Rearranged the code : Created individual packages for everyone and placed their code in the respective package
Main activity and other classes which affect all the classes were not rearranged.

The icon for newsfeed in navigation drawer was changed.
NewsFeed works well with volley library added to the libraries folder.
Manifest was changed by adding a tag android:name for the application
some classes have been added to my part
added fragment support for newsfeed, maximum lines to display, and check network status.
News individual list item click partially implemented
